Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- So they let you sit here?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No fees at all? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be spacious and I could place a stall here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of filming an episode of Street Cry here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be overcrowded. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making a show called Street Cry 4.0.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's ok. Mrs. Hang is easy-going.\N- I'm afraid the crowd would cause inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Hang won't mind. She is very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Hang is the owner of \Nthe plastic store right next to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there may not be enough space here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more spacious when the surrounding stalls close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, there are other stalls around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it'd be better to film in the afternoon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Granny Dan is famous in Phan Thiet, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course.\N- Many people in the market tell me about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows about her and her difficult life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's why they usually offer her food.\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the philanthropists that \NI don't have to starve. Look at the noodles and milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sell up to 160 servings per day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They adore her and often help her get more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Hang usually stands up for me\Nwhen I get treated unfairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I use the donated food efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that your legs are hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have bow legs so I can't walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- I can only move around by holding onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have to sit on a cart and \Nask her to push me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can't walk at all?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make 1 or 2 steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Which leg?\N- They curve outwards at the knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, both of your legs are bowed out so you can't move.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The bow legs make me unable to walk properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I sit on her cart and she would give me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- How do you move around at home?\N- I can hold onto the wall and the furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who makes the sweet soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Me.\N- Oh, I see. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny offers 3 types of sweet soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The business is not very good these days\Nthough I only offer 3 types.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dau Xanh Danh (Mashed Mung Bean Sweet Soup).
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- All goes at VND5,000 per serving?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh gosh, how much profit do you make\N per serving? Like VND1,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,OMG! VND5,000 per serving is too cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- The profit per serving is only a few hundred VND.\N- Not even VND1,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people tell me to increase the price to\N VND6,000 - 7,000 per serving but I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- You should. The cost of living keeps rising up these days.\N- Yeah, but I don't have many customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually receive rice from the philanthropists.\NI only have to earn money to buy medicines
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and some food like fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get about VND100,000 if sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess your maximum daily profit is VND100,000, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- Around that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If the business is good, I can make up to VND120,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I make no profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never think of quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can't stand staying at home and doing nothing.\N- Let your kids take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:14:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Or count on the neighbors.\N- Yeah, but I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Working makes me feel happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Her children don't support her financially.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- I see.\N- They would provide her some food though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But many people are supporting you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes. I've received lots of rice and stuff.\N- I see. You just love doing your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'll work until I can't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep doing my job as long as I'm able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was torture to stay at home during the pandemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if the sales are slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still better than being stuck at home.\NMaybe I'm used to being busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, she's been selling sweet soup for almost half a century.\N- Nah, more than 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- When you were 30 years old?\N- No, I was only 27 when I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do before selling sweet soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I sold iced tea at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I also offered noodles and congee.\NI sold all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I did everything I can.\NI sold iced tea in my neighborhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,at my house. I could do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I didn't mind anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been selling sweet soup here for more than 40 years. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to stick with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, she's determined to earn money on her own.
